<br>
    Level 51 in the Ocean of Tears, is the famous island of Seafury Cyclops, Gornit, and Quag Malstrom.  You will see necromancers, druids, and magicians soloing here.  What elese will you see?  Generally, after the mob is dead, you will see all three medding after the fight... except if the I am the magician in question.  Using chaining pet tactics, I can take down a seafury cyclops and end the fight with MORE mana than I started, allowing me to pull immediately after I have looted the corpse.  If I am running particularly high on mana, I can kill pet and use a nuke to finish off the clops for full experience, resummon a pet, and continue pulling.  I don't think I have seen any other solo class accomplish this feat,on this particular mob.<br>
<br>
    Contrast this with necromancers fear kiting the Allizewsaur, where the magician has a hard time soloing him at ANY level, yet the necro can do it and be at full mana by the time he repops.<br>
<br>
    The soloing abilities of a given class are completely situational, and also depend on the skills of the person at the keyboard. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uxirondarkstar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xiron Darkstar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333333>(12/16/01 3:57:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=73.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_smile.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: mag</span><hr size=1> Yup! Gotta love that quad-kiting! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showMessageRange?topicID=73.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showPrevMessage?topicID=73.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showNextMessage?topicID=73.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=73.topic&index=25><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.threadControl?topicID=73.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=73.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to